####Playing Cards#####

Simple, playing cards game writting in PHP.
To execute the script : 
run: php index.php <user_input>

Result:

run: php index.php 2 
C-A,H-X,S-8,C-6,D-Q,H-8,D-8,H-2,H-Q,C-X,D-5,H-A,S-Q,C-9,S-5,S-K,D-A,H-9,C-7,D-4,D-X,H-7,S-4,S-X,H-J,D-9
